{"tid":1110973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入來聽個好消息，地鐵唔會再壞！","createTime":"2019-04-16T18:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T21:49:44.000Z","uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"912e148508ec00f1211cf120ccfae068ccf06580","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"已經有晚打整合、開過post<br />\n<br />\n以往幾次發生大爭議性嘅政治事件<br />\n<br />\n只要noise大，前前後後一兩日地鐵就會出事<br />\n<br />\n信號系統故障、總機reboot<br />\n<br />\n太多巧合就唔係巧合啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ancuEAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FancuEAM.png&h=1ebf48a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地鐵停一停，搵少好多錢，豬仔又嘈無得返工！<br />\n<br />\n政府身為大股東又要象徵式罰錢，變相有加無減！<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例通過前夕，港共使少少錢就轉移大眾視線<br />\n<br />\n黃賓穎許志安功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持你地"},{"pid":"a43d41ed5696580604384ee845f48687f1e8ea93","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:54:21.000Z","msg":"有人覺得太洗版<br />\n<br />\n但總會有幾隻唔講政治嘅隱性五毛話：<br />\n<br />\n我關心時事，同時關心娛樂新聞、台灣風化post快點強姦我、關心外國貓貓狗狗被虐 要一人一信抗議 都得啫！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以同步進行囉！</span><br />\n鍵盤打幾隻字以為救到香港？一尾得個屌字！<br />\n你又做過咩呀？上連登打兩隻字就叫做實事呀？<br />\n<br />\n多得呢種契弟，五毛唔使開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試問你地一日會睇幾多個post? <br />\n如果長期熱門係呢堆垃圾post，我唔太相信群眾焦點會focus係應該關注嘅事上面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每多一件事一個post出現，就會降低睇到應被關注事件嘅可能性。<br />\n南韓係個好例子，一出事總會用花邊新聞轉移視線，「同時關心唔得咩？一定要對立？」我屌你老母啦！"},{"pid":"06757cce8ce880e0ffa1ea3d30d3b9f29971f713","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:55:26.000Z","msg":"等沉底<br />\n<br />\n我愛黃心穎！狗鐵唔需要再壞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0199a1df7a3778fcd7f00f8d83963d64f62fef","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"哪怕只有一個人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6636eb1a88e0e22d28e9d8881eaa08cda8f2698a","tid":1110973,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:04:18.000Z","msg":"我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺係咁。"},{"pid":"fe8c80c13beea7a3bd5ac2d5c6b88bc45c3e5fb9","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6636eb1a88e0e22d28e9d8881eaa08cda8f2698a","tid":1110973,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:04:18.000Z","msg":"我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺係咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:07:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人理《逃犯條例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1110458\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1110458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請移玉步 有懶人包"},{"pid":"ea3d695858877812b379218827e532fddec49818","tid":1110973,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}